message.content: Based on the process list extracted from the memory image, the "alg.exe" process (PID 2024) is most likely responsible for the initial exploit. The "alg.exe" process is not a common system process and could potentially be used as a disguise for malicious activities. Further analysis of the memory image should be conducted to investigate the activities and interactions of the "alg.exe" process to confirm its involvement in the suspected exploit.
